  Publisher: Penguin Books
Format: Verse
By: Hafiz
Title: Just in Case You Slip
Description: January 24
---
Few can escape self-made traps.

And when a person falls into one, it is natural to call out for help.

If you attend such a plea, take someone like me along as a safety rope
or ladder ...

just in case you slip.
